  "description": "A 4-bed duplex apartment with views and a plunge pool!\n\nCasa Cerro Blanco is a penthouse that offers modern, Scandinavian-styled living and boasts exceptional views over the neighborhood, of the mountains, and the Mediterranean Sea.\n\nUpon entry, you find the open plan living room and kitchen with a dining area right beside as well as a gorgeous wine cabinet to suit. Spaciously designed and with contemporary furnishings this area is wonderfully lit and bright with direct access to a terrace. On this lower terrace, you also have an additional outdoor dining area to enjoy your meals with the calm Mediterranean breeze whenever you’d like!\n\nThe kitchen is fully equipped, featuring an American-style fridge/freezer, and central island/bar, and high-spec appliances.\n\nOn the entrance level, there are 2 bedrooms. The first with 2 single beds and the second with a double bed. These bedrooms also have access to bathrooms on the same level and are beautiful in design and decoration.\n\nHeaded upstairs, you find the Master Bedroom which is stunning! An ensuite bathroom with a rain shower and walk-in closet, complete with a massive round mirror behind a long countertop on the edge of the room, giving the room a unique feel to it. There is one more bedroom on this level which is another double bed ensuite.\n\nOn the upper-level terrace, you have a cozy chill-out spot with some sun loungers, seating, a “fire table”,  and a private plunge pool to bask in the sun in privacy, not to mention the views!\n\nThere is of course AC throughout, Sonos sound system, Wi-Fi, and an allocated parking space in the garage, with direct access to the Penthouse.\n\nThe communal grounds are wonderfully kept. There is a very large pool with a smaller kids’ pool, surrounded by tropical gardens. There are tennis courts to enjoy too, all within the secure gated complex.\n\nThe location of the villa is ideal; In the heart of Marbella’s most popular Nueva Andalucia area right beside Centro Plaza, making it ideal for those who enjoy golf and the comforts and luxury of Puerto Banus and Marbella.\n\nThe area of Nueva Andalucia features some of the town’s best restaurants, pool clubs, bars, nightlife, golf clubs and a choice of supermarkets. In just a few minutes’ drive you could be in Puerto Banus, Marbella old town, San Pedro or simply on the beach.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you.",
